# Backend Environment Variables

## Required Variables

### Database
```bash
# PostgreSQL connection string
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://localhost:5432/apkzio

# Enable database persistence (default: false, uses in-memory storage)
USE_DATABASE=false
```

### Port
```bash
PORT=3001
```

### Service Keys
```bash
# ApkZio service key for SDK authentication
APKZIO_SERVICE_KEY=sk_live_demo_apkzio_local

# Admin API key for dashboard authentication
APKZIO_ADMIN_API_KEY=your_admin_key_here
```

### Admin Auth
```bash
# Enforce admin key for /api/admin/* routes (0 = off, 1 = on)
ENFORCE_ADMIN_AUTH=0
```

## Optional Features

### Stripe Billing
```bash
# Get from https://dashboard.stripe.com/apikeys
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_xxxxxxxxxxxxx
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_xxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Get from https://dashboard.stripe.com/products
STRIPE_PRICE_PRO_MONTHLY=price_xxxxxxxxxxxxx
STRIPE_PRICE_PRO_YEARLY=price_xxxxxxxxxxxxx
STRIPE_PRICE_BUSINESS_MONTHLY=price_xxxxxxxxxxxxx
STRIPE_PRICE_BUSINESS_YEARLY=price_xxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Admin dashboard URL for checkout redirects
ADMIN_URL=http://localhost:5173
```

### Firebase (for FCM push notifications)
```bash
FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your-project-id
FIREBASE_CLIENT_EMAIL=firebase-adminsdk@your-project.iam.gserviceaccount.com
FIREBASE_PRIVATE_KEY="-----BEGIN PRIVATE KEY-----\n...\n-----END PRIVATE KEY-----\n"
```

### Email (Resend)
```bash
RESEND_API_KEY=re_xxxxxxxxxxxxx
RESEND_FROM_EMAIL=noreply@yourdomain.com
```

### Proxy
```bash
# Trust X-Forwarded-* headers (for production behind reverse proxy)
APKZIO_TRUST_PROXY=1
```

## Setup

1. Copy this template:
   ```bash
   cp .env.example .env
   ```

2. Fill in your values

3. Never commit `.env` to git (already in `.gitignore`)

## Verification

Check your configuration:
```bash
npm run dev
```

Visit http://localhost:8787/api/status to see which features are enabled.
